Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.45,0:00:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,圓頂遊樂園  我來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.03,0:00:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好多人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.41,0:00:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.58,0:00:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,一起坐「閃電海豚」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.01,0:00:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那什麼  我查了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.07,0:00:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,先得從摩天輪坐起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.16,0:00:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,然後是雲霄飛車對吧……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.01,0:00:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,真是奇怪的組合
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.23,0:00:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼就突然跑這裡來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.96,0:00:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,遊樂園？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.54,0:00:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我父母收到了免費券
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.43,0:00:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,哇  好想去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.67,0:00:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,把安曇也叫上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.01,0:00:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.64,0:00:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,再叫上比良  四人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.72,0:01:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,遊樂園？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.47,0:01:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,報名報名  我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.85,0:01:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,票不夠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.32,0:01:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼嘛  AA制  如何
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.63,0:01:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,真的假的  我當天有練習賽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.15,0:01:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去夏威夷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.43,0:01:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我問一下永原他們去不去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.96,0:01:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,人越多越好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.01,0:01:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.76,0:01:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.94,0:01:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不過人多也蠻開心的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.85,0:01:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,有單人乘客在候車嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.98,0:01:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我我我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.81,0:01:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不是多個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.50,0:01:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.38,0:01:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,萬歲  一路順風  萬歲  一路順風
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.41,0:01:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,浪漫……
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.23,0:01:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,多個人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.85,0:01:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他是有多想坐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.85,0:01:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,請隨我前往站台
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.92,0:01:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,請站在白線後方的黃箭頭上候車
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.78,0:01:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,吶  安曇  一起坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.72,0:01:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.38,0:01:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,吶吶  節子  玩完之後去那什麼吧  那什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.05,0:01:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,呀？你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.47,0:01:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,-不好  要發動了  -我是說真的啊  來一發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.63,0:01:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不好不好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.07,0:02:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不好不好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.38,0:02:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.27,0:02:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,別說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.38,0:02:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.14,0:02:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,都喊你別說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.54,0:02:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,安曇君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.10,0:02:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.63,0:02:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你怕不怕這些啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.63,0:02:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  一點不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.92,0:02:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,衝下去的時候記得喊「萬歲！圓頂遊樂園！」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.72,0:02:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,準備  要下去了要下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.25,0:02:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,萬歲！圓頂遊樂園！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.03,0:02:37.60,OPJP,,0,0,0,,なんとなく頭の中で君が  離れなくなっていたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.03,0:02:37.60,OPCN,,0,0,0,,不知為何  你的身影一直縈繞在我的腦海
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.37,0:02:58.33,OPJP,,0,0,0,,途切れの会話だね いつも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.37,0:02:58.33,OPCN,,0,0,0,,我們倆的對話總是斷斷續續呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.33,0:03:05.96,OPJP,,0,0,0,,息も吐き出せないほどのことを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.33,0:03:05.96,OPCN,,0,0,0,,和你交談時  我總覺得呼吸困難
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.96,0:03:09.18,OPJP,,0,0,0,,目が合った瞬間に
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.96,0:03:09.18,OPCN,,0,0,0,,在眼神交會的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.18,0:03:19.02,OPJP,,0,0,0,,また何かが胸を貫いてゆく  今!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.18,0:03:19.02,OPCN,,0,0,0,,我感覺彷彿有什麼擊中了我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.02,0:03:26.23,OPJP,,0,0,0,,大好きな人がイマココに居る、居るんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.02,0:03:26.23,OPCN,,0,0,0,,現在我最喜歡的人就在我眼前  在我眼前啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.23,0:03:33.16,OPJP,,0,0,0,,最高の毎日は恋の晴れパレーパレード
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.23,0:03:33.16,OPCN,,0,0,0,,每天都幸福得像戀愛大遊行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.16,0:03:39.96,OPJP,,0,0,0,,近づきたい 誰よりも君に今、いま以上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.16,0:03:39.96,OPCN,,0,0,0,,我想靠近你  我想靠得比誰都近
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.96,0:03:50.51,OPJP,,0,0,0,,会いたくて会いに行く  笑顔また見つけに行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.96,0:03:50.51,OPCN,,0,0,0,,我想見你  我現在就去尋找你的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,萬歲  歡迎回來  萬歲  歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.41,0:04:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,萬歲萬歲  歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.10,0:04:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,爽死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.05,0:04:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到你這麼怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.88,0:04:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,比想像中的可怕多了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.67,0:04:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.93,0:04:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.07,0:04:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,超爽的  好想再坐一次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.16,0:04:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,等玩完別的再坐就得了唄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.34,0:04:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜親沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.70,0:04:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.83,0:04:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你很怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.94,0:04:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,水喝多了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.21,0:04:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那個……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.43,0:04:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,萬歲  可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.41,0:04:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你好配啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.41,0:04:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.71,0:04:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.54,0:04:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,乾脆買了唄  小太
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.05,0:04:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,算了  買不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.76,0:04:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,比良  跟你好配啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.71,0:05:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜親  你們買一對嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.55,0:05:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.05,0:05:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,來來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.07,0:05:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,比良  比良
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.63,0:05:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,要拍囉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.83,0:05:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺有點……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.38,0:05:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.03,0:05:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.43,0:05:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,挺配的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.34,0:05:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,別說了  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.87,0:05:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,啊咧？  浪漫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.27,0:05:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才人還在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.96,0:05:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,有單人乘客在候車嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.41,0:05:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我我我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.72,0:05:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,浪漫就不必擔心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.54,0:05:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.96,0:05:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我出去找找
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.54,0:05:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.45,0:05:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,翹毛君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.01,0:05:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,找到浪漫了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,沒  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.23,0:06:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,對了對了  你看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.21,0:06:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.10,0:06:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,這什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.05,0:06:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我想著或許能當做紀念就……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.74,0:06:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,就這樣也可以？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.74,0:06:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,可以可以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.16,0:06:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,西尾眼睛都閉上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.36,0:06:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,叫我千夏就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.25,0:06:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.07,0:06:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都這麼叫的  男生也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.71,0:06:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,可是……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.96,0:06:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我能叫你小太嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.94,0:06:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.70,0:06:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,小太  小太小太小太
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.47,0:06:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,來  你也叫一下我試試
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.22,0:06:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,千……千夏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.74,0:06:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,根本聽不見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.61,0:06:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,再叫一次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.18,0:06:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,算啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.96,0:06:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,吶  大家說該去挑下一個了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.58,0:06:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  嗯  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.90,0:06:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(374.4,846.6)}遊樂園用群
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.87,0:07:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz19.48\pos(561.6,714.6)}我在醫務室
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.05,0:07:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,蛤？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.09,0:07:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz337.9\pos(921.6,457.8)}醫務室
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.09,0:07:04.41,Notes2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(866.4,786.6)\frz347.3}需要醫務服務的遊客請按下右邊的對講機按鈕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.09,0:07:04.41,Notes2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1168.8,995.4)\frz353.9}東京圓頂遊樂園
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.16,0:07:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.98,0:07:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那個……我是山科浪漫的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.01,0:07:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  請進
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.16,0:07:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.02,0:07:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,小太
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.98,0:07:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼了  怎麼跑醫務室來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.72,0:07:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,中暑？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.77,0:07:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不好好補充水分可是很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.07,0:07:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,休息好了再回去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,記得提醒你朋友補充水分哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.41,0:07:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,明白
